OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1967FThe Old Man of Hoy airs on BBC
OL,7,FOne.
OL,8,
OL,9,FChris Brasher introduces the outside
OL,10,Fbroadcast from the treacherous pillar
OL,11,Fof crumbling sandstone rising 450 feet
OL,12,Fout of the sea off the islands of
OL,13,FOrkney.
OL,14,
OL,15,FIt features Chris Bonington and Tom
OL,16,FPatey climbing the east face and Joe
OL,17,FBrown, Ian McNaught Davis (later
OL,18,Fpresenter of Micro Live), Pete Crew and
OL,19,FDouglas Haston, climbing the south
OL,20,Fface.
